{"tid":1560211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺台灣讀書 想成立基金幫喺台灣嘅義士","createTime":"2019-09-11T06:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:12:16.000Z","uid":258069,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ac5798ab291aacd68fc376ad6feb00c29ec51893","tid":1560211,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的我係台灣讀書嘅學生嚟<br />\n之前發夢畀狗亂拉過搞到差少少要著草走<br />\n嗰時我都算好彩<br />\n屋企肯借錢畀我走<br />\n而且我有Hall住<br />\n有居留證所以冇簽證問題<br />\n（最後告唔入可以正常咁返台灣）<br />\n<br />\n但係好多義士就冇咁好彩屋企冇人幫<br />\n然後612基金又麻撚煩<br />\n（淨係抄ID 呢下其實我都唔多妥 雖然我拎到錢）<br />\n見到之前嗰個義士上嚟求救個心都痛撚埋<br />\n所以想成立一個基金幫呢班義士<br />\n<br />\n入正題<br />\n技術上有好多問題<br />\n- 唔可以用香港個人戶口收錢<br />\n- P牌仔加路人甲冇公信力<br />\n- 點樣揾嗰班義士出嚟<br />\n等等<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉 唔想義士變Condom <br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"faae1fd1d65d3ab54cdcf923471848727b0b34a1","tid":1560211,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"推唔逳呀"},{"pid":"e85d958fe9197b7faef2fba4c158cbefce959516","tid":1560211,"uid":122217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:20:24.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7c2d653b999c828d5c8bc743a20e19957e4ff0","tid":1560211,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"第一 搵個有知名度有公信力既人去睇你盤數"},{"pid":"31fd51a2a6a129acbc3644b6859b7fdd3a59368b","tid":1560211,"uid":296088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05a3be8a63d997b79c1bc14e07a6c90c08a0fbdf","tid":1560211,"uid":163865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:22:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"318512fdd3aa12454280ad66e61c039262b45cea","tid":1560211,"uid":264865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T06:27:05.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n我都好想幫到台灣嘅手足。"},{"pid":"034e7d1aef04e454a15eb6f8d005b3bb72fa5d30","tid":1560211,"uid":258069,"lik