r: red;\">但係兩種acc都違反晒terms of service！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n班狗想分散投資，不過我地要port到佢一條不留！<br />\n<br />\n祝大家舉報愉快<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yxr6aC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yxr6aC.jpg&h=ab2b926e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqeBKbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqeBKbL.jpg&h=93c8393e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82c9c5edc66f07a657282db1bc882f241e383660","tid":1560211,"uid":250944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"我都係台灣讀書<br />\n想幫下義士們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4c1698d9070fb15cbf5b876e608f18f7059a96","tid":1560211,"uid":24413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:27:01.000Z","msg":"你本身已經有佢哋嘅聯絡方式？如果你無，你會用咩方式去搵佢哋出嚟？我同一啲朋友都想課金幫吓佢哋，但係我哋完全唔知點樣可以從一個可信任嘅途徑捐款"},{"pid":"dd0343b7d66d95caadc6dd55adaf9243afbbeff0","tid":1560211,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cec8e7dbf3abac3babfef6384ac532aeb987ff","tid":1560211,"uid":258069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d4c1698d9070fb15cbf5b876e608f18f7059a96","tid":1560211,"uid":24413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:27:01.000Z","msg":"你本身已經有佢哋嘅聯絡方式？如果你無，你會用咩方式去搵佢哋出嚟？我同一啲朋友都想課金幫吓佢哋，但係我哋完全唔知點樣可以從一個可信任嘅途徑捐款"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"冇 我都想揾返佢哋 睇下點樣幫<br />\n一係放個tlg 同台灣電話出嚟叫人揾 （好似杏林嗰啲噉<br />\n課金方面我有諗過 <br />\nPaypal <br />\nBitcoin <br />\n開個台灣銀行戶口畀人過<br />\n<br />\n繼續拋磚引玉"},{"pid":"71b54c7ab1abfe32f29189616e7f6d767714cc1c","tid":1560211,"uid":258069,"like":0,"disli